  "description": [
    "Where Theres a Will Theres a Way This is an old and very true saying and in nothing does it apply with more force than in the matter of saving money While times are prosperous advantage should be taken by every one to save some part of his earnings as it is not what you earn but what you save that makes wealth Dont let the month get by without op ening an account with Montgomery Bank Trust Co E E Forbes Piano Co Montgomery Ala Sept 10 1906 To all teachers of music We beg leave to call your at tention to the fact that we have a new and most com plete stock of Music Teachers supplies sheet music studies and in a word EVERYTHING IN MUS IC We will appreciate a visit or a letter from you Your inquiries as well as orders will receive our best attention Remember that we give big discounts on all music to teachers and that our stock includes the very best teaching pieces published With best wishes for a successful year We are very truly yours E E FORBES PIANO CO Are built to satisfy exact ing workmen They are perfect"
  ],
